01:42:04.300 --> 01:42:08.800
So please come on out,
Cindy and Elizabeth.

01:42:22.040 --> 01:42:23.510
Please join me in
thanking them again

01:42:23.510 --> 01:42:25.510
for an amazing, amazing night.

01:42:25.510 --> 01:43:02.090
